OL,3,CHistoric Manchester mill to be
OL,4,C'partially demolished' after massive
OL,5,Cblaze
OL,7,FAn historic Manchester mill is to be
OL,8,Fpartially demolished after being
OL,9,Fwrecked by a massive blaze.
OL,11,FThe Hotspur Press building, next to
OL,12,FOxford Road railway station, caught
OL,13,Ffire on Monday 23 June, with flames
OL,14,Fand smoke seen right across the city.
OL,16,FThe major incident saw trains
OL,17,Fcancelled, main roads closed and more
OL,18,Fthan 180 residents evacuated from
OL,19,Fnearby high-rise buildings as
OL,20,Femergency services battled to bring
OL,21,Fthe flames under control.
