OL,7,FAt the height of the fire, more than
OL,8,F20 fire engines, two aerial units and
OL,9,Fmore than 100 firefighters were
OL,10,Fworking at the scene, with some
OL,11,Fworking overnight to extinguish the
OL,12,Fblaze.
OL,14,FDuring the incident, the fire spread
OL,15,Fto several balconies at the two tower
OL,16,Fblocks at number 1 Cambridge Street.
