OL,7,FA spokesperson for Greater Manchester
OL,8,FFire and Rescue Service (GMFRS) said:
OL,9,F"Firefighters continue to work hard to
OL,10,Fbring the fire at Hotspur Press to a
OL,11,Fsafe conclusion. Alongside Manchester
OL,12,FCity Council, Greater Manchester
OL,13,FPolice and partners, a decision has
OL,14,Fnow been made to partially demolish
OL,15,Fthe Hotspur Press building over the
OL,16,Fcoming days.
