OL,7,F"This is to enable safe firefighting
OL,8,Fand excavation in areas that are
OL,9,Fcurrently inaccessible, mitigating any
OL,10,Frisk to life. This will also allow
OL,11,Fsafe internal investigations to begin."
OL,13,FDrone footage of the aftermath of the
OL,14,Ffire at Hotspur Mill
OL,16,FThe Victorian building was originally
OL,17,Fbuilt as Medlock cotton mill in around
OL,18,F1801 and is considered Manchester's
OL,19,Foldest mill.
