OL,7,FIn May 2024, Manner, the company who
OL,8,Fhave owned the building since 2020,
OL,9,Fhad a planning application, to turn
OL,10,Fthe The Hotspur Press into a 37-storey
OL,11,Fblock of student flats, unanimously
OL,12,Fapproved by Manchester City Council.
OL,14,FThe plans were delayed due to changes
OL,15,Fin the design, but the company
OL,16,Fannounced in May 2025 that it was
OL,17,Fplanning to submit fresh proposals.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
