OL,4,C'partially demolished' after massive
OL,5,Cblaze
OL,7,FManner, who had vowed to "preserve the
OL,8,Ficonic Percy Brothers signage" and
OL,9,F"restore much of the existing brick
OL,10,Fexterior," has been approached by ITV
OL,11,FNews for comment.
OL,13,FA full investigation is underway to
OL,14,Festablish the cause of the fire.
OL,16,FIt is unknown how many people are
OL,17,Fstill unable to return to their flats
OL,18,Fon Cambridge Street.
